              I&apos;ve worked across <strong style={{ color:"var(--accent3)" }}>cab booking platforms</strong>, <strong style={{ color:"var(--accent3)" }}>HR management systems</strong>, <strong style={{ color:"var(--accent3)" }}>fleet management tools</strong>, and <strong style={{ color:"var(--accent3)" }}>staff management panels</strong> √¢‚Ç¨‚Äù all live, production-deployed applications.
