              <p style={{ fontFamily:"'Space Mono',monospace", fontSize:13, color:"var(--accent)", fontStyle:"italic", lineHeight:1.7 }}>
                &quot;From Development to Production Deployment √¢‚Ç¨‚Äù I Deliver Complete Scalable Solutions.&quot;
